      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of August 16 Business Day article about bid for Avis Group Holdings by Henry Silverman, chief executive of CendantCorporation</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article in Business Day on Wednesday about a bid for Avis Group Holdings by Henry Silverman, chief executive of the CendantCorporation, misstated the amount paid by Cendant in 1999 to settle accusations of accounting fraud. It was $2.8 billion, not $2.8 million.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>An article in Business Day on Wednesday about a bid for Avis Group Holdings by Henry Silverman, chief executive of the CendantCorporation, misstated the amount paid by Cendant in 1999 to settle accusations of accounting fraud. It was $2.8 billion, not $2.8 million.</p>
      </block>
